column2: select top #  P.objid, S.specobjid,      P.ra as sdss_ra, P.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec,     P.psfmag_u as u, P.psfmag_g as g, P.psfmag_r as r, P.psfmag_i as i,P.psfmag_z as z,  W.w1mpro as w1, W.w2mpro as w2, W.w3mpro as w3, W.w4mpro as w4 from wise_xmatch as X     join wise_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr     join photoTag as P on X.sdss_objid = P.objid  join SpecObj as S on S.bestobjid = P.objid where g < # and w4 <= # and w4 >= # and w1 - w2 > #
